<br>
Quite often when policy towards flaming is discussed, people bring up worst case scenarios such as the ones you describe above.  In my experience, such scenarios seldom develop, even on boards with minimal rules.  In a small community such as this one where everone knows everyone else, I really don't think you're going to have a great deal of trouble dealing with flaming and the like.  I would guess that almost all of the problems that may arise could be solved simply by reasoning with the individuals involved.<br>
<br>
I think the central idea is that this board is no longer owned by one self-serving individual; it is owned by the entire community.  Slipstream now exists for the community and for the community alone, not to line pockets or stroke egos.  Once we realize that fact, I think it becomes obvious that you can't rely on a small clique of mod enforcers to make sure that SS remains an enjoyable place to post, you must rely on yourselves.  Every single person should take responsibility for the community.  Every person should feel it is their personal responsibility to treat others with respect, and to intervene when they see others not acting with respect.  After all, if you were to start senseless flaming now, you aren't hurting Christian's bottom line or disrespecting self-important mods or wounding Lisa's ego; all you'd be doing is hurting yourselves and your own communtiy.  I think once people realize that, they'll be far more willing to respect others without being forced to. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bslipstreambbs12353.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wordinterrupted>WordInterrupted</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://site.voila.fr/secondarynexus/delphica2.jpg?0.6518819063405716" BORDER=0> at: 1/19/03 12:09:18 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#001B55><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bslipstreambbs12353.showUserPublicProfile?gid=heroicfool>HeroicFool</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.freeavatars.net/vpimages/reggoofy/fhrgmj106.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Administrator</span><br>  Posts: 278<br> <font color=#EFD68C>(1/19/03 3:05:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm21.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=30.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.freeavatars.net/vpimages/reggoofy/fhrge121.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="ht