mm has come up with an excellent idea for dealing with things like this.  In chat last night she suggested that we move this sort of thing to the Black Hole and then start a discussion (set to sticky) in the forum that the problem took place in. Put a link to the thread in question in the discussion, then we let the members decide what do with the thread.  <br>
<br>
